headline: Coinbase Falls As Bitcoin Continues To Face Resistance; Is The Stock A Buy Now?
summary: Coinbase fell more than 2% on Thursday amid a two-day losing streak.  Is Coinbase stock a buy or sell now?  On MarketSurge charts from Investor's Business Daily, Coinbase stock has undercut its 200-day moving average.

headline: What the crypto world will be listening for when Trump's SEC pick testifies
summary: The crypto industry will be listening closely when Paul Atkins, President Donald Trump’s pick to run the SEC, testifies before a Senate committee Thursday during his nomination hearing.
